dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Crevison Peak and Howard Ranch quadrangles, Merced, Santa Clara, and Stanislaus Counties, California
dct_alternative_sm: Crevison Peak and Howard Ranch map
Geology Crevison Peak and Howard Ranch quadrangle
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Crevison Peak, CA 1955 photorevised 1971, AMS 1758 II NW -- Series V895; Howard Ranch, CA 1999, NIMA 1758 II NE -- series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
Includes "pertinent references", most recent published in 1975.
